org.mpxj

Interface TimeUnitDefaultsContainer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CombinedCalendar, ProjectCalendar, ProjectProperties, TemporaryCalendar

    public interface TimeUnitDefaultsContainer
    Classes implementing this interface provide access to the defaults used when converting duration time units.
